::Prowl::

Prowl raises an eyebrow at Iron Raptor's comment, a bit hurt of her opinion 
of him, even if he knew it was a joke.

"I might be ugly," he says to Feline. He wasn't ugly, but he was just going 
along with Iron Raptor's teasing, "But she's heavy as a truck. Try flying her 
somewhere!"

He frowns, looking at Feline. "Are you allright?"
